dct_title_s: Brookwood in Jackson Township, New Jersey 1961
dct_description_sm: Map of Brookwood, Jackson Township, Ocean County, N.J. along with inset map of township. Map features three tables of curve data and official approvals and signatures from eight different planning board and civil engineering officials.
